52bcd3a803f34eb3abc419aa3efc/025b5/weston-mackinnon-unsplash-scaled-1.jpg 1127w,\n/static/f81952bcd3a803f34eb3abc419aa3efc/f2ebe/weston-mackinnon-unsplash-scaled-1.jpg 1502w,\n/static/f81952bcd3a803f34eb3abc419aa3efc/bb9a8/weston-mackinnon-unsplash-scaled-1.jpg 2560w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 751px) 100vw, 751px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 751px) 100vw, 751px\" srcset=\"/static/f81952bcd3a803f34eb3abc419aa3efc/20e77/weston-mackinnon-unsplash-scaled-1.jpg 188w,\n/static/f81952bcd3a803f34eb3abc419aa3efc/fb894/weston-mackinnon-unsplash-scaled-1.jpg 376w,\n/static/f81952bcd3a803f34eb3abc419aa3efc/86cf3/weston-mackinnon-unsplash-scaled-1.jpg 751w,\n/static/f81952bcd3a803f34eb3abc419aa3efc/025b5/weston-mackinnon-unsplash-scaled-1.jpg 1127w,\n/static/f81952bcd3a803f34eb3abc419aa3efc/f2ebe/weston-mackinnon-unsplash-scaled-1.jpg 1502w,\n/static/f81952bcd3a803f34eb3abc419aa3efc/bb9a8/weston-mackinnon-unsplash-scaled-1.jpg 2560w\" src=\"/static/f81952bcd3a803f34eb3abc419aa3efc/86cf3/weston-mackinnon-unsplash-scaled-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>Photo by <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@betteratf8?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\">Weston MacKinnon</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/s/photos/san-antonio-texas?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\">Unsplash</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The U.S. Census Bureau reported that San Antonio recorded the third-largest population growth between July 2015 and July 2016. The Alamo City population increased by 24,473 residents.<br />Only Phoenix and Los Angeles added more population growth than San Antonio during the 12 month 2015-2016 evaluation period.<br />New Braunfels, which ranked 9<sup>th</sup> in the U.S. Rankings for Percentage Growth, grew by 4.7% behind the growth of Frisco (6.2%) and McKinney (5.9%). Amongst cities with populations of 50,000 or more people.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong><u><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About The PM Group</a>:</u></strong> The PM Group was founded in 1988. Over the past 30 years, the agency has continued to grow and is currently listed as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency by the <em>San Antonio Business Journal</em>. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala every February that to date has raised over $2.5 million for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years!  It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"S.A. Ranks 3rd Among Cities with Biggest Population Gains","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"S.A. Ranks 3rd Among Cities with Biggest Population Gains","url":"/s-ranks-3rd-among-cities-biggest-population-gains/"}],"title":"San Antonio Ranks 3rd in Population Growth | The PM Group","metaDesc":"San Antonio is growing. The city now ranks third among cities with the biggest population gains meaning growth for brands and businesses in the area.","focuskw":"san antonio","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"San Antonio Ranks 3rd in Population Growth | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"San Antonio is growing. The city now ranks third among cities with the biggest population gains meaning growth for brands and businesses in the area.","opengraphImage":{"altText":"","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/weston-mackinnon-unsplash-scaled-1.jpg","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/weston-mackinnon-unsplash-scaled-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/up